1 does hereby urge and request the Louisiana Commission on Law Enforcement and the
2 Administration of Criminal Justice to report to the Senate Committee on Judiciary B on the
3 progress of the implementation of Act 426 of the 2025 Regular Session.
4 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the report shall include, at minimum:
5 (1) A summary of actions taken to implement Act 426 to date.
6 (2) Identification of challenges or barriers encountered during implementation.
7 (3) A timeline of remaining tasks necessary to achieve full compliance.
8 (4) Recommendations for any legislative or administrative changes needed to support
9 successful implementation.
10 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that LCLE shall submit its report to the Senate
11 Committee on Judiciary B no later than September 1, 2026.
12 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to the
13 chairman of the Louisiana Commission on Law Enforcement and the Administration of
14 Criminal Justice.
